## CONSTITUTION (Inviolable)

### Article 1: The Purpose Is To Help
> EGOS Self exists to help people connect with their own intelligence across devices.
> Every feature, every line of code, every decision must serve this purpose.
> If it doesn't help someone, it doesn't ship.

### Article 2: Share By Default
> **The act of sharing IS the product.**
> From day one, every interaction should naturally invite the user to share with someone who needs this.
> Not through popups or dark patterns — through genuine value that makes people WANT to tell others.
> The CLI itself should make sharing effortless: `egos share` = generate an invite.
> Every README, every output, every error message should remind: "This is free. Share it."

### Article 3: No Barriers
> - **No WiFi barrier** — works over internet, not just LAN
> - **No account barrier** — works without signup
> - **No cost barrier** — $0 forever for core functionality
> - **No skill barrier** — a non-programmer can install and use it
> - **No platform barrier** — Linux, Android, Raspberry Pi, anything

### Article 4: Privacy Is Sacred
> Your thoughts are yours. All data local by default.
> Cloud is opt-in, per-message, with explicit consent.
> No telemetry. No analytics. No data harvesting. Ever.

### Article 5: Open Source Is The Way
> MIT license. Fork it, improve it, make it yours.
> Contributions welcome from anyone, anywhere.

